## 1. What SENTRI Does

SENTRI is a Discord security and moderation bot designed to help protect staff identity in Discord servers. Depending on your configuration, SENTRI may:

- monitor member joins and nickname/display-name changes;
- compare member names against protected staff or owner names;
- rename members whose names appear to impersonate protected members;
- store server-specific protected role and whitelist role settings;
- provide dashboard and command-based configuration tools.

SENTRI is not a replacement for human moderation, Discord's own moderation systems, or your responsibility to manage your server.

